title: Let Jeremy Renner Bite Your Kid's Shoulder
itunes:title: Let Jeremy Renner Bite Your Kid's Shoulder
description:
Coronavirus can't slow down JRVP. Anthony, Gregg and Erica venture out to social distance together to go over the week, child support payments, parties, and how Anthony is losing his mind. What super hero would you let expose themselves and not be upset?
